---
import '../styles/components/About.css';
---
<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>About Zigi Code</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h3 class="about-subtitle">The Solo Powerhouse</h3>
        <p class="about-text">
          I am <strong>Nemanja Stanojevic</strong>, the sole engineer behind Zigi Code. In traditional software agencies, projects are passed down through accounts and managers, eventually landing on junior developers. At Zigi Code, you work directly with a senior-level engineer from architecture to deployment.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          I craft robust, performant solutions with a focus on code readability, test coverage, and modern architectural principles. By combining high-performance frameworks like Astro, Next.js, and Swift with serverless, containerized, and secure cloud backends, I help businesses scale with low-latency interfaces.
        </p>
        <div class="about-pillars">
          <div class="pillar">
            <span class="pillar-icon">⚡</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Performance First</h4>
              <p>Optimizing metrics for perfect Web Vitals scores and rapid loads.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <span class="pillar-icon">🛡️</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Secure by Design</h4>
              <p>Ensuring end-to-end data integrity, secure APIs, and robust auth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-stats-panel glass-panel">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number gradient-accent">10+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years of Experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number gradient-accent">50+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Systems Shipped</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number gradient-accent">100%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Direct Communication</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number gradient-accent">99.9%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Availability Target</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
